erformed\",\"performing\"]','[\"went\",\"was\",\"performed\"]','Mixed','2025-09-17 15:13:58.000'),('ca0d1f0a-93bf-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Mixed-14','During the weekend, I __________ my room and __________ my clothes. Then, I __________ some time reading a book.','[\"clean\",\"cleaned\",\"cleaning\",\"organize\",\"organized\",\"organizing\",\"spend\",\"spent\",\"spending\"]','[\"cleaned\",\"organized\",\"spent\"]','Mixed','2025-09-17 15:13:58.000'),('d1bc7e44-8401-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Daily Routine','Every morning, I __________ up at 7 a.m. Then I __________ breakfast and __________ to school. My sister __________ coffee, but I __________ tea.','[\"wake\",\"have\",\"go\",\"drinks\",\"drink\"]','[\"wake\",\"have\",\"go\",\"drinks\",\"drink\"]','A1','2025-08-28 14:26:19.000'),('fe017c84-93bf-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Mixed-B1B2-1','Last year, I __________ on a business trip to London. I __________ many meetings and __________ notes for my manager.','[\"go\",\"went\",\"going\",\"attend\",\"attended\",\"attending\",\"take\",\"took\",\"taken\"]','[\"went\",\"attended\",\"took\"]','Mixed','2025-09-17 15:15:25.000'),('fe019534-93bf-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Mixed-B1B2-2','During the workshop, participants __________ different tasks. I __________ a report and __________ suggestions for improvement.','[\"do\",\"did\",\"doing\",\"write\",\"wrote\",\"writing\",\"provide\",\"provided\",\"providing\"]','[\"did\",\"wrote\",\"provided\"]','Mixed','2025-09-17 15:15:25.000'),('fe0196c4-93bf-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Mixed-B1B2-3','In the conference, my team __________ a presentation about sustainability. We __________ data from several sources and __________ conclusions.','[\"prepare\",\"prepared\",\"preparing\",\"collect\",\"collected\",\"collecting\",\"draw\",\"drew\",\"drawn\"]','[\"prepared\",\"collected\",\"drew\"]','Mixed','2025-09-17 15:15:25.000'),('fe0197d2-93bf-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Mixed-B1B2-4','Last weekend, I __________ my friends at the park. While they __________