pact on the lives of lower-class people, but less the stories about upper-class political confrontations.\",\"Stories about the upper classes and their political differences have not received much emphasis from historians in recent years, while more emphasis has been put on the economic and social developments that have affected the lives of lower-class people.\",\"The economic and social factors that shape the lives of lower-class people have often been emphasized by historians in recent years, since stories about the upper classes and their political quarrels no longer receive any attention.\",\"In recent years, historians have placed less emphasis on stories about the upper classes and their political conflicts, but more on the economic and social forces that shape the lives of lower-class people.\"]','d','\"Doğru çeviri: Son yıllarda tarihçiler, üst sınıflar ve onların siyasi çatışmalarına ilişkin öykülere daha az, ancak alt sınıf insanlarının yaşamlarını biçimlendiren iktisadi ve toplumsal güçlere daha çok vurgu yapmışlardır.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('67100946-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','The question of how changes in the environment give rise to the subjective experience of time in our brains continues to preoccupy psychologists and brain researchers.','[\"Psychologists and brain researchers have recently started to wonder how changes in the environment cause the brain to experience time subjectively.\",\"The question of how changes in the environment give rise to the subjective experience of time in our brains continues to preoccupy psychologists and brain researchers.\",\"The subjective time experience of our brains resulting from environmental changes has long been a controversial issue among psychologists and brain researchers.\",\"The reasons behind the subjective perception of time by the brain have not yet been explained by psychologists or brain researchers.\"]','b','\"Doğru çeviri: Çevredeki değişikliklerin, beyinlerimizde zaman