ını ölçer.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('670ff7bc-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','As Dr. Fawcett has demonstrated in his latest article, it is the underdeveloped countries that have been worst hit by the economic recession.','[\"Son makalesinde Dr Fawcett’in belirttiği gibi, azgelişmiş ülkelerdeki ekonomik durgunluğun etkisi çok yaygındır.\",\"Dr Fawcett’in son makalesinde de belirttiği gibi, azgelişmiş ülkeler ekonomik durgunluktan en çok etkilenenlerin başında geliyor.\",\"Ekonomik bunalım nedeniyle ekonomileri sarsılan azgelişmiş ülkeler Dr Fawcett’in son makalesine konu oldular.\",\"Son makalesinde Dr Fawcett’in açıkladığı gibi, ekonomik durgunluktan en kötü biçimde etkilenenler, azgelişmiş ülkelerdir.\"]','d','\"Doğru çeviri: Son makalesinde Dr Fawcett’in açıkladığı gibi, ekonomik durgunluktan en kötü biçimde etkilenenler, azgelişmiş ülkelerdir.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('67100252-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','With its driverless subways, $25,200 per capita income and smoothly running business centres, Singapore is among the most westernized cities in Asia.','[\"With its driverless subways, $25,200 per capita income and smoothly running business centres, Singapore is among the most westernized cities in Asia.\",\"One of the most westernized cities in Asia is Singapore, for it has driverless subways, $25,200 per capita income and smoothly running business centres.\",\"It is because of the driverless subways, $25,200 per capita income and smoothly running business centres that Singapore is one of the most westernized cities in Asia.\",\"The reason why Singapore is regarded as one of the most westernized cities in Asia is that it has driverless subways, $25,200 per capita income and smoothly running business centres.\"]','a','\"Doğru çeviri: Sürücüsüz metroları, kişi başına düşen 25.200 dolarlık millî geliri ve tıkır tıkır işleyen ticaret merkezleri ile Singapur, Asya‘nın en Batılılaşmış şehirleri arasındadır.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('67100518-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Unless further steps are taken to dismantle their extensive nuclear arms, the Arctic may become a nuclear front again for Russia and the US.','[\"Unless further steps are taken to dismantle their extensive nuclear arms, the Arctic may become a nuclear front again for Russia and the US.\",\"In order for the Arctic to become a nuclear front again, something must be done to reduce the vast amount of nuclear weapons of Russia and the US.\",\"If nothing further is done to dismantle the extensive Russian and US nuclear arms, the Arctic could once again become a nuclear front.\",\"Whether or not the Arctic is to become a nuclear front again, Russia and the US must reduce their nuclear arms.\"]','a','\"Doğru çeviri: Eğer Rusya ve Amerika’nın yoğun nükleer silahlarını ortadan kaldırmak için daha fazla bir şey yapılmazsa, Kuzey Kutup bölgesi yeniden bir nükleer cephe haline gelebilir.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('67100702-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','In recent years, historians have emphasized more the economic and social forces that have an impact on the lives of lower-class people, but less the stories about upper-class political confrontations.','[\"In recent years, historians have emphasized more the economic and social forces that have an impact on the lives of lower-class people, but less the stories about upper-class political confrontations.\",\"Stories about the upper classes and their political differences have not received much emphasis from historians in recent years, while more emphasis has been put on the economic and social developments that have affected the lives of lower-class people.\",\"The economic and social factors that shape the lives of lower-class people have often been emphasized by historians in recent years, since stories about the upper classes and their political quarrels no longer receive any attention.\",\"In recent years, historians have placed less emphasis on stories about the upper classes and their political conflicts, but more on the economic and social forces that shape the lives of lower-class people.\"]','d','\"Doğru çeviri: Son yıllarda tarihçiler, üst sınıflar ve onların siyasi çatışmalarına ilişkin öykülere daha az, ancak alt sınıf insanlarının yaşamlarını biçimlendiren iktisadi ve toplumsal güçlere daha çok vurgu yapmışlardır.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('67100946-8e3b-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','The question of how changes in the environment give rise to the subjective experience of time in our brains continues to preoccupy psychologists and brain researchers.','[\"Psychologists and brain researchers have recently started to wonder how changes in the environment cause the brain to experience time subjectively.\",\"The question of how changes in the environment give rise to the subjective experience of time in our brains continues to preoccupy psychologists and brain researchers.\",\"The subjective time experience of our brains resulting from environmental changes has long been a controversial issue among psychologists and brain researchers.\",\"The reasons behind the subjective perception of time by the brain have not yet been explained by psychologists or brain researchers.\"]','b','\"Doğru çeviri: Çevredeki değişikliklerin, beyinlerimizde zamanın öznel biçimde algılanmasına nasıl yol açtığı sorusu, ruhbilimcileri ve beyin araştırmacılarını düşündürmeye devam etmektedir.\"',4,'e6eec0bb-827c-4a91-b0fb-540f12289300'),('677ded1a-8e97-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','The train will be leaving in _____ 25 minutes.','[\"barely\",\"approximately\",\"entirely\",\"mainly\",\"partially\"]','approximately','\"Doğru kullanım: approximately 25 minutes (yaklaşık 25 dakika).\"',3,'d475b5bf-9c5e-4b8f-a462-40a9e5132dd1'),('677e1240-8e97-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Our English teacher is always so _____ about punctuality.','[\"reluctant\",\"widespread\",\"arrogant\",\"controversial\",\"strict\"]','strict','\"Strict abo