.',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a184102-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','You ........ take a taxi to the airport. I am not busy at the moment. I ........ give you a lift.','[\"mustn’t / will\",\"needn’t / will\",\"needn’t / would\",\"mustn’t / would\"]','needn’t / will','“needn’t” = gerek yok, “will” gelecekte gönüllü eylem belirtir.',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a1842ba-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','I ........ know the exact date of the awards ceremony and neither ........ my partner.','[\"didn’t / neither\",\"don’t / so\",\"didn’t / so\",\"don’t / neither\"]','don’t / so','Olumlu cümlede “so does my partner”, olumsuzda “neither ...”.',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a184440-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','During the meeting one of our colleagues asked the chairperson ........ . The chairman replied “as soon as possible”.','[\"if we had started the new project\",\"when we would start the new project\",\"when we had started the new project\",\"if would we start the new project\"]','when we would start the new project','Dolaylı (reported) soru → would + V.',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a184652-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','I remember ........ London when I was 6 years old and once again I will be there on business next week; I am looking forward ........ the city again.','[\"visiting / to see\",\"to visit / to see\",\"visiting / to seeing\",\"to visit / seeing\"]','visiting / to seeing','“remember + Ving” geçmiş anı; “look forward to + Ving”.',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a1847b0-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A: Bruce is going to Tibet to learn yoga! B: Oh, that sounds interesting, ........ ?','[\"doesn’t it\",\"isn’t it\",\"doesn’t that\",\"isn’t that\"]','doesn’t it','“That sounds interesting” → tag: doesn’t it?',1,'8b412a01-bc73-48da-adef-2c6e6d92a00a'),('7a184940-8b2a-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','The swimmer was very tired but he ........ finish the race and then he ........ on the ground.','[\"c