ent much of his early life.','[\"when / which\", \"where / who\", \"that / whose\", \"where / that\", \"which / who\"]','where / who','\"Where\" yer bildirir, \"who\" insanları tanımlar; Leonardo da Vinci örneğinde doğru kullanımdır.',2,'031d2262-a41b-475c-bee1-e9a5a439ba5a'),('df25e3cc-abc0-11f0-a718-e9d776cb9790','The damage ---- much less if the necessary precautions ---- before the earthquake in 1999.','[\"could be / took\", \"will be / are taken\", \"would have been / had been taken\", \"could have been / had taken\", \"would be / were taken\"]','would have been / had been taken','3. tip koşul (past unreal conditional) → geçmişte gerçekleşmemiş durum ve sonucu.',2,'031d2262-a41b-475c-bee1-e9a5a439ba5a'),('df25e8cc-abc0-11f0-a718-e9d776cb9790','Alex is in his last year at university now. After he ---- with a B.A. this year, he ---- his master’s degree in Germany.','[\"graduated / will start\", \"has graduated / had started\", \"is graduating / started\", \"will graduate / is starting\", \"graduates / is going to start\"]','will graduate / is starting','Gelecek planı + eğitim süreci; “will graduate” ve “is starting” uygundur.',2,'031d2262-a41b-475c-bee1-e9a5a439ba5a'),('df25fe52-abc0-11f0-a718-e9d776cb9790','If she ---- a time machine, she ---- back to the past. She wants to see how people lived in the past.','[\"has / will go\", \"had / will go\", \"has / goes\", \"had had / would have gone\", \"had / would go\"]','had / would go','2. tip koşul (present unreal conditional) → hayali durum için “had / would go”.',2,'031d2262-a41b-475c-bee1-e9a5a439ba5a'),('df260370-abc0-11f0-a718-e9d776cb9790','The house ---- when the landlord ---- the new tenants to show the house.','[\"ought to be painted / had brought\", \"could paint / has been brought\", \"has to paint / is brought\", \"has been painted / is bringing\", \"was being painted / brought\"]','was being painted / brought','Geçmişte bir süreçte yapılan eylem → “was being painted / brought”.',2,'031d2262-a41b-475c-be