INSERT INTO `ReadingPassage` VALUES ('05d95cd2-949d-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Morning Exercise','Every morning, Sarah goes jogging in the park. She usually runs for thirty minutes. After jogging, she stretches her muscles and drinks water. Sometimes, she meets friends who join her for a short walk. Regular exercise keeps Sarah healthy and energetic for the day.','B1','2025-09-18 17:37:37.000'),('0db05a0a-949d-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Grocery Shopping','Tom went to the supermarket to buy groceries. He bought bread, milk, eggs, and some fruits. At the counter, he realized he forgot to buy cheese. He returned to the cheese section and picked it up. Finally, he paid for everything and went home.','B1','2025-09-18 17:37:50.000'),('130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Cooking a New Recipe','Last weekend, I tried cooking a new pasta recipe. I followed the instructions carefully and chopped all the vegetables. I added spices and simmered the sauce for twenty minutes. The aroma filled the kitchen and made me hungry. When I tasted the dish, it was delicious. Cooking this recipe taught me new skills and boosted my confidence. I plan to try more recipes next month. Sharing food with family and friends is always enjoyable.','B1','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c512c-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Cycling Tour','Yesterday, I went on a cycling tour around the countryside. The weather was sunny and warm. I rode through small villages, forests, and fields of flowers. I stopped at a café to rest and drink some water. I met other cyclists on the road and shared travel tips. Cycling helps me stay fit and enjoy nature. At the end of the tour, I felt tired but happy. I hope to plan another tour soon.','B1','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130d5cca-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Attending a Concert','Last Friday, I attended a music concert with my friends. The band played many popular songs and the crowd sang along. The lights and sound effects made the experience amazing. I danced and enjoyed the rhythm of the music. We bought snacks and drinks before the concert started. I felt excited and energetic throughout the event. Attending concerts is a fun way to relax after a busy week. I hope to go to another concert soon.','B1','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130d89de-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Volunteering','I volunteer at a local animal shelter every weekend. I help feed the animals, clean their cages, and walk dogs. I also assist with adoption events and fundraising. Volunteering gives me a sense of satisfaction and purpose. I meet other volunteers who share the same passion. It teaches me teamwork and responsibility. I enjoy spending my weekends helping animals. I hope more people join and support the shelter.','B1','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130db256-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Using Technology','Technology is part of our daily life. I use my computer and smartphone for studying, social media, and communication. I also use apps to organize my schedule and learn new skills. Sometimes, technology can be distracting, so I try to limit screen time. Learning new tools helps me stay efficient and creative. I enjoy discovering innovative solutions and online resources. Responsible use of technology is important for personal and professional growth. I believe technology improves our lives if used wisely.','B1','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('17c43ece-94cc-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – A Trip to the Park','On Sunday afternoon, I went to the park with my cousin. We played on the swings and ran on the grass. There were many flowers and tall trees. We also ate ice cream near the fountain. It was a fun day.','A1','2025-09-18 23:14:34.000'),('17c4ef36-94cc-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My Dog','I have a dog named Max. He is brown and white and has a long tail. Max likes running in the garden and playing with a ball. Every morning, I give him food and water. He is my best friend.','A1','2025-09-18 23:14:34.000'),('17c51d30-94cc-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – At the Cinema','Last Friday, I went to the cinema with my friends. We watched a funny movie and laughed a lot. After the movie, we ate popcorn and drank cola. The cinema was big and full of people. It was a great evening.','A1','2025-09-18 23:14:34.000'),('17c5a7c8-94cc-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My Classroom','My classroom is large and bright. There are twenty desks and a big whiteboard. We have posters of animals and maps on the walls. Our teacher sits at the front of the class. I like studying there with my friends.','A1','2025-09-18 23:14:34.000'),('17c62aea-94cc-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – A Cold Winter Day','It was very cold yesterday. I wore my jacket, scarf, and gloves. The ground was white with snow. My friends and I made a snowman and threw snowballs. After playing, we drank hot chocolate at home.','A1','2025-09-18 23:14:34.000'),('19b11d80-949d-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Movie Night','On Friday evening, Mike and his friends decided to watch a movie at home. They prepared popcorn, drinks, and some snacks. During the movie, they laughed a lot and discussed the plot. After the movie, they played a board game and then talked about their favorite scenes. Finally, they cleaned up the room and went to bed. It was a fun evening for everyone.','B1','2025-09-18 17:38:11.000'),('1d23cc2c-94d1-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Working in a Café','I started working in a café two months ago. My main job is to take orders and serve drinks. Sometimes, I help the kitchen staff with small tasks. I enjoy meeting new people and talking with customers. The café is usually very busy in the mornings. I have learned how to work quickly and stay organized. My boss is very friendly and teaches me new skills. Working here has made me more confident and responsible.','B1','2025-09-18 23:50:30.000'),('1d24618c-94d1-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Traveling by Train','Last weekend, I traveled by train to visit my grandparents. The journey took three hours, and I enjoyed watching the countryside. I read a book and listened to music during the trip. On the train, I met a friendly lady who shared her travel experiences with me. When I arrived, my grandparents welcomed me warmly. We spent the day walking in the garden and having lunch together. Traveling by train is relaxing and gives time to think and observe the world. I hope to travel by train again soon.','B1','2025-09-18 23:50:30.000'),('1d24e1d4-94d1-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Volunteering at the Animal Shelter','Every Saturday, I volunteer at a local animal shelter. I help feed the dogs and cats and clean their cages. Sometimes, I take the animals for a short walk outside. I also assist with adoption events and meet people who want to adopt pets. Volunteering is hard work but very rewarding. I have learned patience and responsibility. I enjoy spending time with animals and making a difference in their lives. I hope to continue volunteering for many years.','B1','2025-09-18 23:50:30.000'),('1d251398-94d1-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Learning a New Language','I decided to learn French last year. I attend classes twice a week and practice speaking with my classmates. At first, it was difficult to understand and remember new words. I use language apps to improve my vocabulary and listen to French songs. My teacher encourages me to speak in class every day. I also write short stories in French to practice writing. Learning a new language is challenging but exciting. I hope to visit France next year and speak with local people.','B1','2025-09-18 23:50:30.000'),('1d253aee-94d1-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Preparing for a School Project','Next week, I have to prepare a school project about renewable energy. I researched different sources like solar, wind, and water energy. I made a presentation with pictures and graphs. My friends helped me find information and practice the presentation. I am a little nervous about presenting in front of the class. I hope the teacher will like our work. Preparing this project taught me teamwork and responsibility. It also made me more confident speaking in public.','B1','2025-09-18 23:50:30.000'),('20991af2-94cb-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My Family','I live with my mother, father, and little sister. My mother is a teacher, and my father is a driver. My sister is only five years old. We often have dinner together in the evening. On Sundays, we go to the park and play games.','A1','2025-09-18 23:07:39.000'),('20ada4f4-94cb-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My House','My house is small but very nice. There are two bedrooms, a living room, and a kitchen. My room has a bed, a desk, and a window. I like reading books on my bed. In the kitchen, my mother cooks delicious meals.','A1','2025-09-18 23:07:39.000'),('20addce4-94cb-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – At the Market','I go to the market with my father every Saturday. We buy fruits, vegetables, and bread. My favorite fruit is banana. My father likes apples. The market is always busy and colorful.','A1','2025-09-18 23:07:39.000'),('20adfba2-94cb-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My School','My school is big and modern. There are many classrooms, a library, and a gym. My favorite subject is English. I like reading books in the library. At break time, I play football with my classmates.','A1','2025-09-18 23:07:39.000'),('20ae2032-94cb-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','A1 – My Best Friend','My best friend is Anna. She is twelve years old. She has short black hair and brown eyes. Anna likes dancing and singing. We go to the same school, and we often do homework together.','A1','2025-09-18 23:07:39.000'),('2184f52c-949d-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','B1 – Weekend Cleaning','Last Saturday, Anna decided to clean her house thoroughly. She vacuumed all the carpets, dusted the shelves, washed the windows, and organized her wardrobe. Her brother helped her clean the kitchen and the living room. After finishing, they felt proud of their work and relaxed by watching TV. They also mad