 Pay → Go home\",\"Pay → Buy items → Pick cheese → Forget cheese → Return → Go home\"]',0,'Correct sequence.','2025-09-18 17:37:50.000'),('130bbcc6-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What did the writer cook?','[\"Pasta\",\"Salad\",\"Pizza\",\"Soup\"]',0,'Pasta.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c26e8-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Translate: \"aroma\"','[\"koku\",\"tat\",\"renk\",\"görünüm\"]',0,'It means koku.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c2b34-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','How long did the sauce simmer?','[\"Twenty minutes\",\"Ten minutes\",\"Thirty minutes\",\"Five minutes\"]',0,'Twenty minutes.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c2c92-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What did cooking teach the writer?','[\"New skills and confidence\",\"Nothing\",\"Only fun\",\"Only patience\"]',0,'New skills and confidence.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c2ddc-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Who does the writer share food with?','[\"Family and friends\",\"Neighbors\",\"Strangers\",\"Colleagues\"]',0,'Family and friends.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130c2f26-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130b3ea4-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','When does the writer plan to try more recipes?','[\"Next month\",\"Tomorrow\",\"Next week\",\"Never\"]',0,'Next month.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130d45fa-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130c512c-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What did the writer do yesterday?','[\"Cycling tour\",\"Swimming\",\"Reading\",\"Shopping\"]',0,'Cycling tour.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130d4c12-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130c512c-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Translate: \"countryside\"','[\"kırsal alan\",\"şehir\",\"ev\",\"okul\"]',0,'It means kırsal alan.','2025-09-18 23:57:23.000'),('130d4e24-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','130c512c-94d2-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Where did the writer ride?',