edness\"','[\"açık fikirli olma\",\"kapalı fikirli olma\",\"meraklı olma\",\"kararsızlık\"]',0,'Correct translation is \"açık fikirli olma\".','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6e7bfde-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e79fcc-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What problem can cultural differences cause?','[\"Misunderstandings\",\"Faster work\",\"More money\",\"No problems at all\"]',0,'They may cause misunderstandings.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6e7c178-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e79fcc-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','How can misunderstandings be reduced?','[\"Through communication and open-mindedness\",\"By ignoring people\",\"By speaking louder\",\"By avoiding new cultures\"]',0,'Communication and open-mindedness are essential.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6e9746e-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e79fcc-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What do governments and organizations promote?','[\"Cultural exchange programs\",\"Sports events only\",\"Expensive hotels\",\"Food festivals only\"]',0,'They promote cultural exchange programs.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6e9775c-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e79fcc-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What do exchange programs help people experience?','[\"Different ways of life\",\"Nothing useful\",\"Only problems\",\"The same culture again\"]',0,'They help people experience different ways of life.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6e978ce-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e79fcc-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','What personal qualities are important for cultural diversity?','[\"Tolerance and respect\",\"Anger and fear\",\"Laziness and silence\",\"No qualities\"]',0,'Tolerance and respect are important.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6ea0fe6-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','f6e9a790-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1fdbf124df','Which renewable sources are mentioned?','[\"Solar, wind, and hydro power\",\"Nuclear and coal\",\"Oil and gas\",\"Wood and charcoal\"]',0,'Solar, wind, and hydro power are mentioned.','2025-09-18 22:59:20.000'),('f6ea159a-94c9-11f0-9a3c-3f1f